      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOLD MINER (1) boasts a strong record this journey here with seven wins and five minors from 19 tries. In the money last time at this track (19.93) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 5.5 lengths third. Rates on top and should go close. HIS FERNANDO (2) has missed the frame at his last two runs but could not have been more impressive the run prior in his brilliant 19.56 win at this track over 340m. Top win three back and rates a key player again. SALAMAT (8) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (20.13) in a Grade 5 at this track. Form here sound including four wins. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Key player if finds best. SWIFT ELI (3) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.",
